{"tid":1580642,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警FB新post又暗叫示威者做曱甴","createTime":"2019-09-19T07:27:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T07:45:01.000Z","uid":276442,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d818ca2c8e439e3b68e14fb2978fe5da904159a8","tid":1580642,"uid":276442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T07:27:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ro8TmDc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRo8TmDc.jpg&h=9919204c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母你話佢地唔撚係特登停係呢個位我唔撚信<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94670a2ee98b637b23a5ce4b36a226727885ecf1","tid":1580642,"uid":5482,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T07:28:50.000Z","msg":"有咩好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c12da56d1eaf3197e41876cf55314f152d8b032c","tid":1580642,"uid":45910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T07:30:41.000Z","msg":"譯埋幅圖做英文啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ba1c560bc7f99053facc2db5a788c44bb2c2fda","tid":1580642,"uid":22121,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T07:30:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rPtW3Tc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrPtW3Tc.jpg&h=d3e20874&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1922a35a7563eb4454fde997e7f62a8b6d9e7026","tid":1580642,"uid":164374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T07:31:05.000Z","msg":"舉報仇恨言論?"},{"pid":"7676a902dbd1fe7cf40e68597fcc242802532855","tid":1580642,"uid":8033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T07:33:48.000Z","msg":"（來自Facebook員工既來信）<br />\n好多人唔知Facebook對D言論點審查，覺得report post都冇用，但係唔知點解鬧下X蟲就俾人ban account。等我話你知個遊戲點玩法。<br />\nFacebook有樣野叫做community standards，全世界都係跟同一指引。當中有講到乜野叫仇恨言論(hate speech)：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/communitystandards/hate_speech\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcommunitystandards%2Fhate_speech&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5dOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=7e59dcf3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/communitystandards/hate_speech</a><br />\n<br />\n其中第一類係包括：&quot;<span style=\"color: red;\">Dehumanizing speech such as reference or comparison to INSECTS</span>&quot;<br />\nFacebook講到明dehumanizing speech係最嚴重：<br />\n&quot;Tier 1, the most severe, involves calls to violence or dehumanizing speech against other people based on their race, ethnicity, nationality, gender or other protected characteristic (&ldquo;Kill the Christians&rdquo;).&quot;<br />\n依度講到明hate speech見一條delete一條：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://newsroom.fb.com/news/2017/06/hard-questions-hate-speech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsroom.fb.com%2Fnews%2F2017%2F06%2Fhard-questions-hate-speech%2F&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5dOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=f814f690\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://newsroom.fb.com/news/2017/06/hard-questions-hate-speech/</a><br />\n<br />\n咁大家知道點解講X蟲會俾人ban啦。<br />\n好啦，而家唔講X蟲，講曱甴。<br />\n依幾日我見到好多港字頭page話示威者係曱甴既post。有D仲用埋錢推post。依度有一個例子：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/SaluteToHKPolice/photos/a.722777894430252/3010528202321865/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FSaluteToHKPolice%2Fphotos%2Fa.722777894430252%2F3010528202321865%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5dOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=5b72959f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/SaluteToHKPolice/photos/a.722777894430252/3010528202321865/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n好簡單，依D post點睇都係dehumanizing speech。Facebook唔只剩係要delete個post，個page出咁多個曱甴post好應該係連個page都要ban埋。"},{"pid":"1dede6008d1eb97de4ac5752251f6ec40ab5ca37","tid":1580642,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T07:40:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"445043a6d93ae8c8f53fbc110d41f8d6ba3efb72","tid":1580642,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T07:41:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"839f86f043fd84195fd15dc2032691f445e2da10","tid":1580642,"uid":13330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T07:42:38.000Z","msg":"洗乜理佢哋d垃圾<br />\n畀心機打國際線打到佢哋跪低"},{"pid":"92241fb577487ae3a3f84d930afe92723f03529e","tid":1580642,"uid":29204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T07:44:01.000Z","msg":"推佢上twitter 啦<br />\n平時就賴某個前線popo情緒不穩<br />\n而家公然係自己page 到咁講<br />\n白紙黑字<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acff09df4f432bad3a6bd8a925286c4b52867eec","tid":1580642,"uid":269194,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7676a902dbd1fe7cf40e68597fcc242802532855","tid":1580642,"uid":8033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T07:33:48.000Z","msg":"（來自Facebook員工既來信）<br />\n好多人唔知Facebook對D言論點審查，覺得report post都冇用，但係唔知點解鬧下X蟲就俾人ban account。等我話你知個遊戲點玩法。<br />\nFacebook有樣野叫做community standards，全世界都係跟同一指引。當中有講到乜野叫仇恨言論(hate speech)：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/communitystandards/hate_speech\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcommunitystandards%2Fhate_speech&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5dOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=7e59dcf3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/communitystandards/hate_speech</a><br />\n<br />\n其中第一類係包括：&quot;<span style=\"color: red;\">Dehumanizing speech such as reference or comparison to INSECTS</span>&quot;<br />\nFacebook講到明dehumanizing speech係最嚴重：<br />\n&quot;Tier 1, the most severe, involves calls to violence or dehumanizing speech against other people based on their race, ethnicity, nationality, gender or other protected characteristic (&ldquo;Kill the Christians&rdquo;).&quot;<br />\n依度講到明hate speech見一條delete一條：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://newsroom.fb.com/news/2017/06/hard-questions-hate-speech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsroom.fb.com%2Fnews%2F2017%2F06%2Fhard-questions-hate-speech%2F&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5dOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=f814f690\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://newsroom.fb.com/news/2017/06/hard-questions-hate-speech/</a><br />\n<br />\n咁大家知道點解講X蟲會俾人ban啦。<br />\n好啦，而家唔講X蟲，講曱甴。<br />\n依幾日我見到好多港字頭page話示威者係曱甴既post。有D仲用埋錢推post。依度有一個例子：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/SaluteToHKPolice/photos/a.722777894430252/3010528202321865/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FSaluteToHKPolice%2Fphotos%2Fa.722777894430252%2F3010528202321865%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5dOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=5b72959f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/SaluteToHKPolice/photos/a.722777894430252/3010528202321865/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n好簡單，依D post點睇都係dehumanizing speech。Facebook唔只剩係要delete個post，個page出咁多個曱甴post好應該係連個page都要ban埋。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T07:45:01.000Z","msg":"我REPORT左好多曱甴POST係hate speech都唔得, 唔知FB咩標準LOR<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}